(119, 'Led by Associate Professor Dr. Joseph Lim, (M.Arch Program Director, NUS Architecture), Soo K. Chan of SCDA and Dr. Hossein Rezai Jorabi, this was a cross-continental studio at the National University of Singapore’s Department of Architecture, involving site visits and studio reviews that took place in New York City.', 'Led by Associate Professor Dr. Joseph Lim, (M.Arch Program Director, NUS Architecture), Soo K. Chan of SCDA and Dr. Hossein Rezai Jorabi, this was a cross-continental studio at the National University of Singapore&#39;s Department of Architecture, involving site visits and studio reviews that took place in New York City.', 1, 0, 119),
