ht=\"332\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Bridge_over_Pond0.jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1275\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-74 col-lg-74 col-md-74 col-xs-74\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Entrance1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"244\" height=\"332\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Entrance0.jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"790\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-192 col-lg-192 col-md-192 col-xs-192 archive_banner\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-118 col-lg-118 col-md-118 col-xs-118\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Pond_details1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"390\" height=\"332\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Pond_details0.jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1275\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-74 col-lg-74 col-md-74 col-xs-74\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Grided_Details1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"244\" height=\"332\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Harbourview_House_Grided_Details0.jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"720\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"archive_intro\">\n<p>—</p>\n<p>The Chicago Athenaeum 2009 International Architecture Awards</p>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/architecture/harbourview-house.html\">Harbourview House</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/\">TDA Architects</a>.</p>\n]]>', '', 0, 0, 556),
