(571, '<![CDATA[<div class=\"col-sm-192 col-lg-192 col-md-192 col-xs-192 archive_banner\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Flat1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"330\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Flat0.jpg\" data-height=\"1059\" data-width=\"1920\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-192 col-lg-192 col-md-192 col-xs-192 archive_banner\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Overview1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"629\" height=\"330\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Overview0.jpg\" data-height=\"1019\" data-width=\"1920\" /></div>\n<div class=\"archive_intro\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>GRANGE ROAD HOUSE I </strong> |  Singapore</p>\n<p>This house at Bishopsgate Road is an elegant dialectic of monolithic and delicate architectural elements. Overall, the expression of the house is a response to the client’s affinity for modern art. Purity is the order of the day and the entire composition forms an unadulterated and clean landscape that provides an ideal backdrop for the client’s personal collection of sculptural art.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-192 col-lg-192 col-md-192 col-xs-192 archive_banner\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\" src=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Love1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"630\" height=\"330\" data-enlarge=\"http://images.scdaarchitects.com/www_scdaarchitects_com/SCDA_Grange_Road_House_I_Love0.jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1635\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-192 col-lg-192 col-md-192 col-xs-192 archive_banner\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-118 col-lg-118 col-md-118 col-xs-118\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-responsive zoom-img\"