(717, '<![CDATA[<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"630\" height=\"330\" class=\"size-full wp-image-225\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1.jpg 630w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-300x157.jpg 300w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-16x8.jpg 16w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-36x19.jpg 36w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-48x25.jpg 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" /><br />\nSOO K. CHAN  |  Principal </p>\n<p>Soo K. Chan is a practicing architect based in Singapore. He is the founding principal and design director of SCDA, a multi-disciplinary firm engaging in architecture, interior, landscape and product design. Mr. Chan is the recipient of several awards, including the inaugural Singapore President’s Design Award, Designer of the Year, the SIA-Getz Architecture Prize for Emergent Architecture in Asia and three RIBA Awards. A graduate of Yale University, Mr. Chan is Professor of Architecture (Practice) at the National University of Singapore.</p>\n<p>SCDA’s portfolio ranges from master planning, resorts and hotels, high-rise luxury residences, commercial and institutional buildings, and private homes spanning Asia/Oceania, Africa, Europe and America. SCDA has more than 120 employees with offices in Singapore, Shanghai and New York. Mr. Chan is currently working on three residential towers in NYC, including 118 East 59th Street, 515 West 29th Street, and Soori High Line.</p>\n<p>Mr. Chan is both the architect and developer of Soori High Line. Soori High Line marks Chan Soo Khian’s third global Soori-branded offering, joining his line of Soori Living furniture for Poliform, and the award-winning Soori Bali. Soori Niseko, a ski resort in Japan, is currently under development.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/about/soo-k-chan-principal.html\">Soo K. Chan, Principal</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/\">TDA Architects</a>.</p>\n]]>', '', 0, 0, 710),
