(1205, '<![CDATA[\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-225\" width=\"287\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1.jpg 630w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-300x157.jpg 300w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-16x8.jpg 16w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-36x19.jpg 36w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1-48x25.jpg 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 287px) 100vw, 287px\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">SCDA is a design studio seamlessly integrating architecture, interiors, landscape and product design to create holistic spatial experiences. Established in 1995 by Founding Principal and Design Director Soo Chan, SCDA was awarded the AIA International and AIA NY Awards for Architecture (2019); inaugural Royal Institute of British Architects Award for International&nbsp; Excellence&nbsp; (2016);&nbsp; the&nbsp; RIBA&nbsp; International&nbsp; Award&nbsp; for&nbsp; OneKL&nbsp; (2012)&nbsp; and&nbsp; the&nbsp; Lincoln&nbsp; Modern&nbsp; (2003); and&nbsp; the&nbsp; SIA-Getz&nbsp; Architecture&nbsp; Prize&nbsp; for&nbsp; Emergent&nbsp; Architecture&nbsp; in&nbsp; Asia&nbsp; (2006),&nbsp; in&nbsp; addition&nbsp; to&nbsp; nine&nbsp; Chicago Athenaeum International Architecture Awards.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"630\" height=\"330\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Soo_K_Chan_SCDA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-225\" sr