(1504, '<![CDATA[\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.competethemes.com/blog/link-image-url-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" fancybox=\"false\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-614\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1.jpg 300w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1-225x300.jpg 225w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1-12x16.jpg 12w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1-27x36.jpg 27w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dennis-normal_R1-36x48.jpg 36w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<h6 style=\"font-size:11px\"><strong>Nguyen Ba Tung</strong><br>Founder &amp; Creative Director TDA ARCHITECT</h6>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"font-size:11px\">Field: Arichitect &#8211; Interior Designer</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\" style=\"font-size:11px\">Experience: <br>&#8211; Work directly and collaborate with architectural and interior design offices in Ho Chi Minh City and Hanoi City as a Senior Designer: interior design office and interior workshop of Gia Viet Interior, project architectural design office of Ecolandgroud, construction design office of C.TECH, hotel project design office of Friend Studio.<br>&#8211; 4 years’ experience as the Founder and Creative Director of HomeDecor3T, now TDA Architect.<br><br>Career Thought and Philosophy:<br>&#8211; Always learn &amp; always be creative.<br>&#8211; Architecture needs a theoretical basis, just like every organism always has a genome.<br>&#8211; Real architecture must reflects society in its own time and predicts the future.<br>&#8211; Architecture needs to be creative and tested in practice.<br>&#8211; In addition to technical creative solutions, architecture needs to participate in social and natural environmental aspects of sustainability.<br>&#8211; People create society &amp; economic development, of which architecture is a part. However, architecture can have a good or bad impact on people and natural landscape, which is up to us.<br>&#8211; Architecture can really bring about a compromise between itself and the human and the natural environment in a sustainable way, from even the smallest aspects to the much larger ones.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns teams\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Hesly_normal_Rev1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-620\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Hesly_normal_Rev1.jpg 180w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Hesly_normal_Rev1-12x16.jpg 12w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Hesly_normal_Rev1-27x36.jpg 27w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Hesly_normal_Rev1-37x48.jpg 37w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px\" /><figcaption><strong>HESLY KUMAAT</strong></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>REGIONAL EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Jason_normal.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-623\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Jason_normal.jpg 180w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Jason_normal-12x16.jpg 12w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020