(675, '<![CDATA[<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"435\" height=\"330\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-337\" srcset=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4.jpg 435w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4-300x228.jpg 300w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4-16x12.jpg 16w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4-36x27.jpg 36w, http://scda.toptrendvn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Phaidon4-48x36.jpg 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" /><br />\nARCHITIZER A+ AWARDS 2016</p>\n<p>A CELEBRATION OF THE 100 PLUS 2016 ARCHITIZER A+AWARD WINNERS AS CHOSEN BY AN INTERNATIONAL JURY OF 300 EXPERTS</p>\n<p>SkyTerrace@Dawson and the National Design Centre in Singapore won the Architizer A+ Jury Award 2016 for Best High-Rise Residential and Best Gallery, and are featured in this publication, exclusive to Phaidon.</p>\n<p>The Architizer A+Awards celebrate the world’s best architecture every year. The winners were singled out amongst entries from over 100 countries by an international jury of over 300 experts and over 200,000 public votes. 60 categories of winners celebrate the diversity of the world’s architecture. There are giant towers, tiny apartments, a sinuous elevated bike path and a human-sized birdhouse. Architecture is everywhere and fulfills endless functions. This book celebrates all of them! </p>\n<p>The A+Awards are run by Architizer.com—the largest online platform for architecture.  Phaidon</p>\n<p>SPECIFICATIONS:<br />\nFormat: Hardback<br />\nSize: 279 x 216 mm, 11 x 8 1/2 in<br />\nPages: 240 pp<br />\nIllustrations: 500 colour illustrations<br />\nISBN: 9780714872872</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/about/architizer-a-awards-2016.html\">ARCHITIZER A+ AWARDS 2016</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://scda.toptrendvn.com/en/\">TDA Architects</a>.</p>\n]]>'),
