(1518, '&#8211; Work directly and collaborate with architectural and interior design offices in Ho Chi Minh City and Hanoi City as a Senior Designer: interior design office and interior workshop of Gia Viet Interior, project architectural design office of Ecolandgroud, construction design office of C.TECH, hotel project design office of Friend Studio.'),
(1519, '&#8211; 4 years’ experience as the Founder and Creative Director of HomeDecor3T, now TDA Architect.'),
